title: The Draymond Green Show - Mateen Cleaves
itunes:title: The Draymond Green Show - Mateen Cleaves
description:
Mateen Cleaves joins ‘The Draymond Green Show’ to discuss why he chose Michigan State over Michigan, what it was like building the program up with Coach Tom Izzo, how his tough times have helped shape him, his bond with his family, and more. #Volume #Herd

Produced by: Jackson Safon
